   <h1>The Troll&#39;s Bane Chronicle</h1>

   <h2>The fifth year of the new era: January</h2>

<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 1st of January, Calilmal Greenleaf announces the birth of a newborn Baby, and names it Avareniah after Avareniah Igdrasil</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 1st of January, Misjilah Mehilao declares the votes for the Elven elders to continue. </P> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age on the 1st of January, The man named "The Executioner" kills Thalodos Artemetus in the name of Moshran.</P> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 2nd of January, Farel announces the man by the name of Patrick has been jailed.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 2nd of January, Julia Fertry is found dead in the forest near Trolls vein. Her possessions are given to Pendar Fayed and his Family.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 2nd of January. A Verbal War between Orcs and Dwarves ends, with Pendar Fayed and Salathe Kankas trying to mediate. It escalates into a declaration of war dispite Pendar and Salathe's valant efforts.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 2nd of January, Gabon Corad declares the war between Orcs and Dwarves continues.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 5th of January, Stephen Rothman seeks a teacher of History, Philosophy, Races, Gods and Honorable Conduct. He is Directed to Scholar Markous.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 6th of January, Saladin Tyrus declares the continuations of lessons at the Magic academy.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 6th of January, Misjilah Mehilaho accuses Durin Silberbart and Friedwulfa of insulting elves within the town walls of Trollsbane</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 8th of January,Friedwulfa declares the offical opening of the Silverbrand market.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 8th of January,Moathia Nethiala, Isilwen Anrion, and Alaine Milan are declared the Elders of Vanima.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 9th of January, Brer Beothach arives and asks his help in searching for his brother, Cliu Beothach.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 9th of January, Stephen Rothman declares that those trying to harm his daughter, Alica and Skyler Rothman, will be hunted down and killed. </p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 10th of January, Derek Corydon Resigns to Overseer of Trollsbane and assigns Bailey Thunnigan as Captain of the Town Guard.</P> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 12th of January, Town Guard Captain Bailey Thunnigan calls out for citizens of Trollsbane to become a guard and protect their loved ones.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 13th of January, The Kingdom of Silverbrand calls out for all dwarves to join it's ranks, They offer protection, a home, and alot of ale along with the citizenship.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 15th of January, Ghorn, King of Silverbrand, Declares that the traitor Gishmel has been executed.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 13th of January, Lennier states for travelers to watch their step, as two demons were found and dispatched outside the grey rose.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 17th of January, Faladron Furnir announces that Ariges the Lich and a Demon were spotted at the south gate, caution is heavily advised.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 18th of January, Eliron Sharid declares his departure from Gobaith</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 19th of January, The Halfling Allen also Declares his departure from Gobaith.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 22nd of January, Dinendal Narmolanya, Co-commander of the Tinichor en Vanima, Warns the Knights of the Grey Rose of a man blantantly stealing books from the Grey rose Library, he is later identified as Ciegan Zain Ibatha</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 23rd of January, Stephen Rothman annouces his wedding between Himself and Bailey Thunnigan, to be held at the Ushara Shrine.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 25th of January, A man named Reverence mocks Dei Gorgeon, for declaring himself a Preist of Ronagan.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 31st of January, Ghorn Gemfist is to be crowned King of Silverbrand, but some Dwarven kin rebel against him, the Corronation is postponed.</p> 
<p>In the 6th year of the new age, on the 31st of January, Stephen Rothman, Durgin, Belgram, Syrana, and Burlok are branded traitors of Silverbrand for rioting against Ghorn Gemfist's rule.</p> 

